but yeah, it's not a bad idea.  Except for the fact that AA effects tied to mana tend to be overpowered compared to other AA effects. (For the simple reason that there are tons of ways to increase your mana/mana regen, but virtually no way to improve the re-use time of other AA abilities.)</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
